cross.datastructures.fragments
Class ImmutableVariableFragment2

java.lang.Object
  cross.datastructures.fragments.ImmutableVariableFragment2
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFragment, IVariableFragment, IXMLSerializable, java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>, java.util.Comparator<IFragment>
public class ImmutableVariableFragment2
extends java.lang.Object
implements IVariableFragment

A class representing Variables. A Variable is a meta-info container for existing data stored in an array for example. VariableFragment objects belong to a parent FileFragment, which corresponds to a virtual file structure.

Author:
Nils.Hoffmann@cebitec.uni-bielefeld.de
